.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
4 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, go, canasta
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, futuristic, craftsman
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the futuristic house is between the owner of the dog and the ranch-style house##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 6. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the farmhouse house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the craftsman house is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
14. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the ranch-style house##8
18. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Game          | canasta     | snooker | scrabble | go  |
| House   | ranch-style    | futuristic  | craftsman | farmhouse |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

