.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, radish, apple, kale
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, mystery, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, electronic, folk, jazz
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, apricot, lilac
 1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 2. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
 3. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 4. the person eating apple is somewhere to the right of the fan of blues##5
 5. the person who likes apricot is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
 6. the person eating kale is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
11. the person watching action movies is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Food         | broccoli    | kale   | apple | radish |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | mystery  | western   | drama      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues    | folk      | jazz       |
