 3. the person eating plum is the musician##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the dancer and the electrician##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 6. the fan of country is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the software-developer##1
10. the electrician is the fan of country##1
11. the fan of soul is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
14. the electrician is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
15. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
