 9. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
10. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the manager##3
11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
13. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the manager##8

