.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, colombian, canadian, chinese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, sports, thriller, spy
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the chinese##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the colombian##8
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the canadian##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the person watching spy movies is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the colombian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | soul      | reggae     | folk     |
| Nationality         | italian | canadian  | chinese     | colombian  |
| Movie-Genre     | drama     | thriller | spy | sports     |

