There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, aquamarine, lilac, black
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person eating cranberry##6
 2. the dancer is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 4. the dancer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 5. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
 8. the person eating asparagus is not to the left of the photographer##8
 9. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person eating nectarine is somewhere between the person who likes black and the project-manager##7
11. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
