 6. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the colonial house##8
 7. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the american##8
 8. the american is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the american and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

